TITLE: Defining Dialog Component with Radix UI in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet defines a Dialog component using Radix UI primitives. It includes props for controlling the dialog's open state, content, and close functionality. The component is styled using CSS modules.
SOURCE: https://github.com/webstudio-is/webstudio-community.git/blob/main/docs/university/radix/dialog.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: TypeScript
